 <span data-ttu-id="e5b68-121">可以通过获取的事件，可以由语音平台基础结构类型<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A>属性上的合成引擎站点实现<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e5b68-121">The type of the events which can be handled by the Speech platform infrastructure can be obtained through the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite.EventInterest%2A> property on the synthesizer engine site implementation of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
